abstract: CNBC is rearranging two of its market hours by canceling two programs and expanding two others in their place.

lead_paragraph: The business news channel CNBC is rearranging two of its market hours by canceling two programs and expanding two others in their place.

headline.main: CNBC Expands Two Programs and Cancels Two Others
